    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/2c946819217c6c3e8ac5b74abdf48e23.avif?t=1771858925\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/55911c92ee0f4118594d37b5dbdc972c.avif?t=1771858925\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放在桌面角落，无论你在工作还是摸鱼，英雄都在不停刷怪打宝！无需操作、不怕打断，全自动战斗带来彻底放松的升级体验。彻底告别传统RPG那种反复跑图、刷怪、点技能的疲惫感，随时点开收菜、强化、进阶副本，轻松享受战力飞升的快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/39d5a7cfc56cec2164bd253720b7a64a.poster.avif?t=1771858925\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/39d5a7cfc56cec2164bd253720b7a64a.webm?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/39d5a7cfc56cec2164bd253720b7a64a.mp4?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/ef0c3c891391b6735c1f8436484c354c.avif?t=1771858925\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款能玩上头的放置RPG——怪自己越变越强，刷怪根本停不下来！自动战斗，从杂兵清怪到Boss冲刺一路横推，装备掉不停、数值涨不停，彻底复刻RPG副本刷宝爽感！击杀、掉落、强化，再加上随机词条和组合效果，挂机就能追求极限神装！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/d5f3eb18c364d2996c7a9261cb2f9f2f.poster.avif?t=1771858925\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/d5f3eb18c364d2996c7a9261cb2f9f2f.webm?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/d5f3eb18c364d2996c7a9261cb2f9f2f.mp4?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/6aa3e90ac520062cbb7eeb61a648f46a.poster.avif?t=1771858925\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/6aa3e90ac520062cbb7eeb61a648f46a.webm?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/6aa3e90ac520062cbb7eeb61a648f46a.mp4?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/55d3173ff428e741e9cd67325fd6f027.avif?t=1771858925\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内设十几种可转职职业，从战士、法师到刺客、召唤、守墓人、炼金术士，每位英雄都拥有独特天赋与成长方向！技能数量超夸张，战斗风格千变万化，既能打出AOE清屏爆发流，也能组合召唤+控制+持续伤害的多段战术体系。自由搭配流派，打造你的最强副本队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/56d98b26eab2f5c4c221a0843a63dd6a.poster.avif?t=1771858925\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/56d98b26eab2f5c4c221a0843a63dd6a.webm?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/56d98b26eab2f5c4c221a0843a63dd6a.mp4?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/41df385202d2c22cc5c254c453416e03.avif?t=1771858925\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复古像素横板画风，致敬经典RPG的热血战斗体验！放在桌面一角，不占空间，不干扰工作学习，但一抬眼就能看到你的冒险小队激战正酣！轻松挂机的外壳下藏着RPG深度成长机制，边挂机边爆装，升级节奏爽感拉满，哪怕只是摸鱼时点开也让人心情爆好！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/6a3efd219dec9350268872f806c8584c.poster.avif?t=1771858925\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/6a3efd219dec9350268872f806c8584c.webm?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/6a3efd219dec9350268872f806c8584c.mp4?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/34ed5593bb4950c68df2208105b06818.avif?t=1771858925\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗采用横板自走棋式，全自动，但每次阵容搭配都充满策略深度！前排抗压、后排爆发、控场联动、主副C协同……数十种技能随机组合，打出超高伤害的Combo爆发或连环控制链，低配翻盘、一波反杀，全靠你的理解和排兵布阵！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/4451cbbf3733b20b66f5e4b2e0345de2.poster.avif?t=1771858925\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/4451cbbf3733b20b66f5e4b2e0345de2.webm?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122460/extras/4451cbbf3733b20b66f5e4b2e0345de2.mp4?t=1771858925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >桌面冒险小队已经组建完毕，即刻开启桌面副本之旅！</p>",
